      </div>
      
      <div class="p-12 text-center space-y-8">
        <!-- Step 1 -->
        <div class="ob-step space-y-6" id="ob-step-1">
          <div class="text-5xl">✨</div>
          <h2 class="text-white font-serif italic text-3xl tracking-tight">Seja bem-vindo.</h2>
          <p class="text-zinc-500 font-sans text-xs leading-relaxed max-w-xs mx-auto">Vamos configurar sua barbearia para o próximo nível em poucos instantes.</p>
          <div class="space-y-4 pt-4 text-left">
            <div class="space-y-1">
              <label class="text-zinc-500 font-sans text-[8px] font-bold uppercase tracking-widest ml-1">Nome do Estabelecimento</label>
          <input type="text" id="ob-name" class="w-full bg-white/5 border border-white/10 rounded-xl px-6 py-4 text-white font-sans text-sm focus:border-primary-container transition-all" placeholder="Ex: BarberPro Matriz">
            </div>
          </div>
          <button onclick="obNext(2)" class="w-full bg-primary-container text-on-primary-container py-5 rounded-xl font-sans text-[10px] font-bold uppercase tracking-widest hover:bg-white transition-all shadow-[0_0_40px_rgba(212,175,55,0.2)]">PrÃ³ximo Passo →</button>
        </div>

        <!-- Step 2 -->
        <div class="ob-step space-y-6 hidden" id="ob-step-2">
          <div class="text-5xl">âœ‚ï¸</div>
          <h2 class="text-white font-serif italic text-3xl tracking-tight">Primeiro Serviço.</h2>
          <div class="space-y-4 pt-4 text-left">
            <div class="space-y-1">
              <label class="text-zinc-500 font-sans text-[8px] font-bold uppercase tracking-widest ml-1">Nome do Serviço</label>
              <input type="text" id="ob-svc-name" class="w-full bg-white/5 border border-white/10 rounded-xl px-6 py-4 text-white font-sans text-sm focus:border-primary-container transition-all" placeholder="Ex: Corte Degradê">
            </div>
            <div class="grid grid-cols-2 gap-4">
              <div class="space-y-1">
                <label class="text-zinc-500 font-sans text-[8px] font-bold uppercase tracking-widest ml-1">Preço (R$)</label>
                <input type="number" id="ob-svc-price" class="w-full bg-white/5 border border-white/10 rounded-xl px-6 py-4 text-white font-sans text-sm focus:border-primary-container transition-all" placeholder="45">
              </div>
              <div class="space-y-1">
                <label class="text-zinc-500 font-sans text-[8px] font-bold uppercase tracking-widest ml-1">Duração (min)</label>
                <input type="number" id="ob-svc-dur" class="w-full bg-white/5 border border-white/10 rounded-xl px-6 py-4 text-white font-sans text-sm focus:border-primary-container transition-all" placeholder="30">
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="flex gap-4 pt-4">
            <button onclick="obNext(1)" class="flex-1 text-zinc-600 font-sans text-[8px] font-bold uppercase tracking-widest hover:text-white transition-colors">Voltar</button>
            <button onclick="obNext(3)" class="flex-[2] bg-primary-container text-on-primary-container py-5 rounded-xl font-sans text-[10px] font-bold uppercase tracking-widest hover:bg-white transition-all shadow-[0_0_40px_rgba(212,175,55,0.2)]">PrÃ³ximo →</button>
          </div>
        </div>

        <!-- Step 3 -->
        <div class="ob-step space-y-6 hidden" id="ob-step-3">
          <div class="text-5xl">✂️</div>
          <h2 class="text-white font-serif italic text-3xl tracking-tight">O Especialista.</h2>
          <div class="space-y-4 pt-4 text-left">
            <div class="space-y-1">
              <label class="text-zinc-500 font-sans text-[8px] font-bold uppercase tracking-widest ml-1">Nome do Barbeiro</label>
              <input type="text" id="ob-barber-name" class="w-full bg-white/5 border border-white/10 rounded-xl px-6 py-4 text-white font-sans text-sm focus:border-primary-container transition-all" placeholder="Ex: João Silva">
            </div>
            <div class="space-y-1">
              <label class="text-zinc-500 font-sans text-[8px] font-bold uppercase tracking-widest ml-1">Especialidade</label>
              <input type="text" id="ob-barber-role" class="w-full bg-white/5 border border-white/10 rounded-xl px-6 py-4 text-white font-sans text-sm focus:border-primary-container transition-all" placeholder="Ex: Barba & Cabelo">
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="flex gap-4 pt-4">
            <button onclick="obNext(2)" class="flex-1 text-zinc-600 font-sans text-[8px] font-bold uppercase tracking-widest hover:text-white transition-colors">Voltar</button>
            <button onclick="obNext(4)" class="flex-[2] bg-primary-container text-on-primary-container py-5 rounded-xl font-sans text-[10px] font-bold uppercase tracking-widest hover:bg-white transition-all shadow-[0_0_40px_rgba(212,175,55,0.2)]">PrÃ³ximo →</button>
          </div>
        </div>

        <!-- Step 4 -->
        <div class="ob-step space-y-6 hidden" id="ob-step-4">
          <div class="text-6xl animate-bounce">🚀</div>
          <h2 class="text-white font-serif italic text-3xl tracking-tight">Pronto para o Sucesso.</h2>
          <p class="text-zinc-500 font-sans text-xs leading-relaxed max-w-xs mx-auto">Sua barbearia está online. Compartilhe o link e comece a agendar agora mesmo.</p>
          <div id="ob-link-box" onclick="obCopyLink()" class="bg-primary-container/5 border border-primary-container/20 rounded-xl p-5 font-mono text-xs text-primary-container break-all cursor-pointer hover:bg-primary-container/10 transition-all">...</div>
          <button onclick="obFinish()" class="w-full bg-primary-container text-on-primary-container py-5 rounded-xl font-sans text-[10px] font-bold uppercase tracking-widest hover:bg-white transition-all shadow-[0_0_40px_rgba(212,175,55,0.2)]">Entrar no Painel ✓</button>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="toast fixed bottom-8 left-1/2 -translate-x-1/2 bg-primary-container text-on-primary-container px-6 py-3 rounded-full font-sans text-[10px] font-bold uppercase tracking-widest shadow-2xl opacity-0 translate-y-4 pointer-events-none transition-all duration-300 z-[1000]" id="toast"></div>




</body>
</html>
